        "## Recommendations for Job Seekers\n",
        "\n",
        "- Target AI Upskilling: Integrate machine learning, generative AI, and agentic capabilities into your current skill set. Even in traditional professions, adding a layer of AI competency unlocks a massive baseline salary premium without requiring a complete transition into foundational AI engineering.\n",
        "- Leverage Geographic Arbitrage: If you live outside of major tech hubs like San Francisco or New York, heavily target fully remote AI positions. Remote market dynamics force employers to align close to competitive national standards, allowing you to maximize a high-tier salary against a lower local cost of living\n",
        "- Navigate Variable Compensation Timelines: If you are targeting highly fluid industries like Travel or Media Production, prepare for total compensation packages dependent on irregular cycles. Anchor your job hunt, contract signings, or bonus structure negotiations around peak industry upswings to maximize immediate payouts.\n"
